<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 18 at 6:12AM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...SLICK TRAVEL EXPECTED THIS MORNING...
An area of snow, sleet and freezing rain will continue over the
area early this morning. Roads will become slick as temperatures
drop to near freezing this morning and slushy snow and sleet
accumulates on area roads. Minor icing will also be possible in
some locations due to the pockets of freezing rain.</description>
